---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About – TrendSeek" description="About TrendSeek: your source for in-depth analysis on trending topics in technology, finance, science, and economy." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="container about-page">
      <h1>About TrendSeek</h1>

      <p><strong>TrendSeek</strong> is your intelligent guide to the topics shaping our world. We deliver in-depth, well-researched articles on the most important trends in <strong>technology, finance, science, and economy</strong> — available in English, Italian, Spanish, and French.</p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>In a world overflowing with information, finding thoughtful and reliable analysis can be challenging. TrendSeek exists to cut through the noise. We combine AI-powered research with editorial quality to bring you articles that are:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Well-researched</strong> — backed by data, studies, and expert insights</li>
        <li><strong>Accessible</strong> — complex topics explained clearly for everyone</li>
        <li><strong>Multilingual</strong> — available in 4 languages to reach a global audience</li>
        <li><strong>SEO-optimized</strong> — easy to find when you need them most</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <p>Our articles span a wide range of trending and niche topics:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🔬 <strong>Science &amp; Technology</strong> — Quantum computing, AI, cybersecurity, emerging tech</li>
        <li>💰 <strong>Finance &amp; Investing</strong> — Options strategies, market analysis, personal finance</li>
        <li>🌍 <strong>Economy &amp; Geopolitics</strong> — Global trends, trade policies, economic shifts</li>
        <li>🚀 <strong>Startups &amp; Entrepreneurship</strong> — Bootstrapping, growth strategies, innovation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>TrendSeek uses a unique blend of artificial intelligence and human curation. Our AI engine identifies trending and niche topics based on real-time search data, then generates comprehensive long-form articles that are reviewed and published across four languages.</p>

      <h2>Stay Informed</h2>
      <p>Bookmark <a href="/">trendseek.net</a> and check back regularly for fresh content. New articles are published daily, covering the latest developments across our core topics.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
        Have questions or suggestions? Reach out at <strong>info@trendseek.net</strong>
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .about-page h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .about-page ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-page li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-page a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
